column5: Anyone enter the contest posted a few months back for a free charter for the musky opener.  Well I did and today I found out I won   Ill be taking two of my good fishing buddys out for 8hrs food, gear and drinks included.  With Mike on the boat I should be able to reduce those thousand casts by a few.  Thanks again to mike at www.reelpro.ca I cant remember his screen name at OFC but im super pumped and wont sleep till the opener.
Congrats and have fun !!!! Can always learn lots on a charter... I know I did.  His screen name here was spam.
That's great!  Congrats and I'm sure you'll have a blast!  Maureen
congrats and have a blast free trips are the best happy
Ouch......play nice Wayne.  The guy was nice enough to offer a trip for the auction......  Sinker
Congrats.  I'm sure you'll have a great time.
I didn't win that prize but I just got an email that told me i've made it through to the second stage of the publishers clearing house sweepstakes!!!!
You can't win if you don't play!
NO it wasn't for the auction Sinker!
